  <prefix>§</prefix>
  <num>25-834</num>
  <heading>Powdered alcohol.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>It shall be unlawful for a person to sell or offer to sell powdered alcohol.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>A licensee under either an on-premises or off-premises retailer's license shall not offer for sale powdered alcohol to a customer.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(c)</num>
    <text>A person who violates this section shall be fined an amount of up to a maximum of $1,000.</text>
  </para>
